            <div type="transcript" id="F787A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Bloom <app type="emendation"><lem>upon</lem><rdg>opon</rdg></app>
 the mountain stated </l>
                    <l>Efflorescence of a sunset </l>
                    <l>Reproduced the same.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Seed had I, my purple sowing</l>
                    <l>Should address the day </l>
                    <l>Not a tropic of a twilight </l>
                    <l>Show itself away - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Who for tilling, to the mountain </l>
                    <l>Come, and disappear -</l>
                    <l>Whose, be this renown, or fading </l>
                    <l>Witness, is not here.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>While I state the solemn petals </l>
                    <l>Far as north and east </l>
                    <l>Far as south and west expanding</l>
                    <l>Culminate in rest -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And the mountain to the evening </l>
                    <l><app type="emendation"><lem>Fits</lem><rdg>Fit</rdg></app>
 his countenance </l>
                    <l>Indicating by no muscle </l>
                    <l>The experience.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
